 The masqutio bots flew seperatly across the world. In the midst of the fight 
one of the masquitos landed on apocalypse. Suked out some of his dna and flew 
off. It would be only felt as a masquito bite. Another landed on killfest. 
Biting into him. So small doubt it could be felt. The two masqutios flew off 
back to the spot of thier master. Another masquito landed on the back of 
Zardus. Took a small sample and flew off quickly. To short of time for most 
bots to tell. Another masquito landed on the back of  Dark Mouse. Takeing its 
sample and flying off. It would only  be known as a bothering insect.   One 
more insect flew and landed on top of the bot known as cerberus. It had used 
its digging abilitys though small to dig a minature hole under the shields. 
So small doubtful that a autogun would target a small creature. It took its 
sample and left. The bots headed to thier new home. The two bots they needed 
last would be obtained later. For now this would be enough to start thier 
master's first evolution.
